cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.PL

This paper discusses the performance evaluation of SDN controllers, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI) and system and control (cs.SY). It also involves benchmarking tools and evaluation criteria, which could be categorized under cryptography and security (cs.CR), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), and programming languages (cs.PL).
